The,service,handles,processing,of,Visa,or,MasterCard,credit,card,payments,either,from,an,application,s,custom,page,or,through,a,secure,page,hosted,by,the,provider,Both,credit,card,and,debit,card,payments,are,processed,and,recurring,payments,can,be,scheduled,API,methods,support,submission,of,transaction,and,cardholder,information,for,debit,cards,or,credit,cards,Returned,data,detail,either,purchase,pre,authorization,status,or,full,payment,processing,outcomes,Methods,also,support,refunds,of,processed,payments,and,related,functions